Perintah Scanning

 

Perintah Nuclei Scan Dasar

nuclei -u target.com (1 Target)

nuclei -l targets.txt (Semua Target Didalam File)

 

Perintah Nuclei Berdasarkan Severity

nuclei -l targets.txt -severity high,critical

 

Perintah Nuclei Berdasarkan Template Folder

 

Perintah Nuclei Only CVE

nuclei -t nuclei-templates/http/cves/ -u target.com

 

Perintah Nuclei All Vulnerability HTTP

nuclei -t nuclei-templates/http -u target.com

 

Perintah Nuclei Misconfiguration

nuclei -t nuclei-templates/http/misconfiguration target.com

 

Perintah Nuclei Exposure

nuclei -t nuclei-templates/http/exposures target.com

 

Perintah Nuclei Scan Lebih Cepat (parallel / performance)

nuclei -l targets.txt -rate-limit 500

500 request per second

 

Perintah 3 Tools

subfinder -d target.com -o subfinder.txt | httpx -l subfinder.txt -o httpx.txt -mc 200 | nuclei -l httpx.txt  -severity low,medium,high,critical -o nuclei.txt -ept ssl

